{"tid":1188014,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"足球根本係矮撚遊戲","createTime":"2019-06-06T04:04:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T10:46:08.000Z","uid":174295,"like":22,"dislike":124,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"d5c3eb351400c493ccb0a255bf56860fed9c9da8","tid":1188014,"uid":174295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T04:04:24.000Z","msg":"歷史上有邊到高佬可做到球王？答案係一個都無！<br />\n<br />\n我求其揾左篇喺香討討論10大球王嘅飛機文嚟睇<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.discuss.com.hk/index.php?action=thread&amp;tid=26624081\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.discuss.com.hk%2Findex.php%3Faction%3Dthread%26tid%3D26624081&d=M59wMjr1KB2wSFKn0iQ%2BghmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=8743311d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.discuss.com.hk/index.php?action=thread&amp;tid=26624081</a><br />\n<br />\n10.朗拿甸奴 1.81m<br />\n9. 迪士堤芬奴 1.78m<br />\n8. 告魯夫 1.83m<br />\n7. 柏天尼 1.78m<br />\n6. 丙朗 1.87m<br />\n5. 真朗拿度 1.83m<br />\n4. 施丹 1.85m<br />\n3. 碧根鮑華 1.81m<br />\n2. 馬勒當拿 1.65m<br />\n1. 比利 1.72m<br />\n<br />\n再計埋現役球王美欺（1.7m)入去，你會發現一半人唔過米八，而且愈矮嘅人仲愈勁，無一個人過到米九可以做到球王<br />\n<br />\n相反，大部分所謂球王根本自欺欺人，唔敢離開温室去nba超戰自己，而依班人分分鐘連控球後衛都做唔到，所以話足球其實係一班現實上嘅loser用嚟打飛機嘅遊戲"},{"pid":"1db890e300412f2aca1a227f125676ece0c24a93","tid":1188014,"uid":46849,"like":116,"dislike":3,"score":113,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T04:05:34.000Z","msg":"NBA 成班力架玩晒<br />\n唔知以為去左非洲熱帶雨森都仲要開冷氣"},{"pid":"02d5c85ff85125d6870e626bc48c182945178b01","tid":1188014,"uid":155902,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T04:06:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9edaa62b25f84f62949a1d640a5b6524e7584f27","tid":1188014,"uid":234509,"like":63,"dislike":1,"score":62,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T04:07:39.000Z","msg":"事實係喺香港打籃球嗰啲都係矮撚<br />\n街場大部分人都唔過米9"},{"pid":"e223d385c34b57a8f135ffb47e11b93992565866","tid":1188014,"uid":98223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit